The brutal incident happened at Mbilwi Secondary School. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A Limpopo teenager will return to court on 20 April for a formal bail application. That's after she briefly appeared in court on Friday. She is accused of assaulting a fellow pupil, Lufuno Mavhunga. READ: Family wants justice for Lufuno Mavhunga The incident was caught on camera. Mavhunga has since died by suicide. A memorial service was held in her honour on Friday.